_______________________________________________________________________________
"Rejuvenation"      
        This is a healing ability that costs time rather than power
        points.  It is cast with a number of minutes, which will be
        spent concentrating.  At the end of that time, the psionicist
        will heal an amount of hit points GREATLY influenced by the
        amount of time spent rejuvenating.  Rejuvenating once for 6
        minutes will restore an exponentially greater amount than doing
        it 3 times for 2 minutes each.  Of course, any commands given
        during the concentration period will cancel the power completely
        and no healing will take place at all.  Note that the mental
        effort necessary to sink into this meditative trance is such
        that no other power may be used during the rejuvenation time,
        even if the psionicist cancels the power.  The rejuvenation cost in
        sp is approximately what would be regenerated normally in the
        same amount of time.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  rejuvenate <number of minutes>
